-----------------------------
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-----------------------------

sendmail_queue.php process the MTA Sendmail or Exim queue to store messages in MailWatch database and see them in the MailWatch GUI.

Copy the sendmail_queue.php file in /usr/local/bin

Edit CRONTAB:

# crontab -e

# Run sendmail_queue.php each minute
0-59 * * * * 	/usr/local/bin/sendmail_queue.php

Note: sendmail_queue.php re-creates all entries on each run, so for busy sites you will probably want to change this to run every 5 minutes or greater.
